    LevelLoader

    creates all game objects for easy instanciation from the LevelFactories all x and y parameters are the lower left corner of the object

    Score

    ScoreDatabase
    Database class for scores, Accessible via singleton pattern
    SwipeEvent
    Represents a swipe event, has position and direction
    TapEvent
    Represents a tap on the screen
    TimingSystem
    With the timing system you can register functions, which are called after a given delay The timing system is updated before the game scene, the timer is reduced by 1 every update If the timer of a registered function reaches 0, it is executed
    TimingSystem.TimedAction  
    WraparoundSystem
    Watches a certain set of entities These entities are teleported to the other side of the screen when they exit the screen
